  "title": "Customer Service Officer",
  "description": "<p>· Attend to walk-in, phone in customers enquires and to promote products and sales.<strong> (There\nwill be incentives and Sales commission on top of basic salary)</strong></p><p>· To listen and understand the customer description of fault on their device and to\nBook-in or process customers’ collection</p><p>· Provide basic QC check (using system or manual testing) to ensure repaired device is in\nworking condition before returning to customer.</p><p>· Provide product support to customers</p><p>· Guide customers on data transferring</p><p>· Ensure all forms are duly filled & signed by customers before booking in device\nfor repair or for collection</p><p>· Ensure service counter & reception area are neat and tidy daily at all time<br /></p><p><u><strong>Location</strong></u></p><p>: Orchard area</p>",
